django-yaturbo installation
===========================
​
​
Python ``pip`` and ``bleach`` packages are required to install ``django-yaturbo``.
​
​
From sources
------------
​
Use the following command line to install ``bleach`` and ``django-yaturbo`` from their sources directories (containing setup.py):
​
    pip install .
​
or
​
    python setup.py install
​
​
From PyPI
---------
​
Alternatively you can install ``bleach`` and ``django-yaturbo`` from PyPI:
​
    pip install bleach
    pip install django-yaturbo
​
​
Use `-U` flag for upgrade:
    
    pip install -U bleach
    pip install -U django-yaturbo

